ey/Joyeuse Erenford</a> <small>(298 AC)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Renly_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Wedding of Renly Baratheon and Margaery Tyrell\">Renly Baratheon/Margaery Tyrell</a> <small>(298 AC)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Tyrek_Lannister_and_Ermesande_Hayford\" title=\"Wedding of Tyrek Lannister and Ermesande Hayford\">Tyrek Lannister/Ermesande Hayford</a> <small>(299 AC)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Roose_Bolton_and_Walda_Frey\" title=\"Wedding of Roose Bolton and Walda Frey\">Roose Bolton/Walda Frey</a> <small>(299 AC)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Tyrion_Lannister_and_Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Wedding of Tyrion Lannister and Sansa Stark\">Tyrion Lannister/Sansa Stark</a> <small>(299 AC)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Red_Wedding\" title=\"Red Wedding\">Edmure Tully/Roslin Frey</a> <small>(299 AC)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Purple_Wedding\" title=\"Purple Wedding\">Joffrey Baratheon/Margaery Tyrell</a> <small>(300 AC)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Petyr_Baelish_and_Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Wedding of Petyr Baelish and Lysa Arryn\">Petyr Baelish/Lysa Arryn</a> <small>(300 AC)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Tommen_I_Baratheon_and_Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Wedding of Tommen I Baratheon and Margaery Tyrell\">Tommen Baratheon/Margaery Tyrell</a> <small>(300 AC)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Lyonel_Corbray_and_Lady_Corbray\" title=\"Wedding of Lyonel Corbray and Lady Corbray\">Lyonel Corbray/merchant's daughter</a> <small>(300 AC)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Ramsay_Bolton_and_Arya_Stark\" title=\"Wedding of Ramsay Bolton and Arya Stark\">Ramsay Bolton/\"Arya Stark\"</a> <small>(300 AC)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Hizdahr_zo_Loraq_and_Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Wedding of Hizdahr zo Loraq and Daenerys Targaryen\">Hizdahr zo Loraq/Daenerys Targaryen</a> <small>(300 AC)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Sigorn_and_Alys_Karstark\" title=\"Wedding of Sigorn and Alys Karstark\">Sigorn/Alys Karstark</a> <small>(300 AC)</small></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404202126\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.050 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.073 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 991/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 16277/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 21157/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 8069/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2610/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.5 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   55.247      1 -total\n 52.21%   28.845      1 Template:Date\n 20.84%   11.512      8 Template:Ref\n 20.46%   11.303      1 Template:Weddings\n 19.45%   10.747      1 Template:Navbox\n 11.62%    6.417      8 Template:Ref/core\n  6.66%    3.679      1 Template:Navbar\n  5.10%    2.816      2 Template:Quote\n  4.64%    2.564      3 Template:Transclude\n  3.79%    2.094      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:39455-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404202126 and revision id 330463\n -->\n",
